    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior retains a strong shine, though it does show minor signs of regular use such as small stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically sound and reliable, this car offers a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
